Pre-Game Insights: Osame Sahraoui and several new players could make their debuts for the Maroc.
Louis Mafouta, a prolific striker, has scored 5 goals in his last three appearances for the Centrafrique.
Raoul Savoy's team is known for their ability to challenge top teams (draws against Mali and Ghana in recent months; victory against Nigeria in 2021).
Others: The match will take place on Saturday, October 12, at 20:00 local time in Oujda.
The match will be televised on Arryadia in Morocco and beIN Sport 2 in France.
